  "texts": [
    "For the table on the left, accuracy is calculated as the percentage of time predicting the correct overall category.",
    "Predicting any of pants-fire, false, or mostly false is correct when the claim is labeled as pants-fire, false, or mostly false.",
    "Conversely, predicting any half-true, mostly true, or true is correct when the claim is labeled as one of these categories.",
    "For the table on the right, accuracy is calculated as the percentage of time predicting the PolitiFact category.",
    "For example, predicting \"half-true\" when the claim is labeled as \"mostly-true\" is treated as a false prediction."
  ],
